# saas-operator-foundation T-02 (FR-07, design §7) — keep this directory in
# git so `shared/seed/saas-operator/` always exists. The directory-iterating
# seed loader (api/scripts/seed-saas-operator.ts) reads every *.json here;
# `.gitkeep` is skipped by its `.json` filter, so a .gitkeep-only directory
# is a clean no-op. The six wave-2 content specs drop <function>.json here.
